rules.description: button4 -> command + shift + open_bracket
button5 -> command + shift + close_bracket
button6 -> command + mission_control
button9 -> command + tab
any + caps_lock -> command + option + control + left_shift
option + c -> escape, c
command + option + control + shift + hyphen -> command + option + eject
command + option + control + shift + equal_sign -> control + shift + eject
command + m -> vk_none
command + h -> vk_none
command + option + control + shift + 1 -> f13
command + option + control + shift + 2 -> f14
command + option + control + shift + 3 -> f15
command + option + control + shift + 4 -> f16
command + option + control + shift + 5 -> f17
command + option + control + shift + 6 -> f18
command + option + control + shift + 7 -> f19
command + option + control + shift + 8 -> f20
command + option + control + shift + 9 -> keypad_0
command + option + control + shift + n -> keypad_1
command + option + control + shift + a -> keypad_2
command + option + control + shift + s -> keypad_3
command + option + control + shift + w -> keypad_4
command + option + control + shift + d -> keypad_5
command + option + control + shift + z -> keypad_6
command + option + control + shift + open_bracket -> keypad_7
command + option + control + shift + close_bracket -> keypad_8
command + option + control + shift + f -> keypad_9
command + option + control + shift + comma -> keypad_comma
command + option + control + shift + period -> keypad_period
command + option + control + shift + up_arrow -> keypad_asterisk
command + option + control + shift + e -> keypad_plus
command + option + control + shift + left_arrow -> keypad_slash
command + option + control + shift + down_arrow -> keypad_enter
command + option + control + shift + right_arrow -> keypad_hyphen
command + option + control + shift + q -> keypad_equal_sign
command + option + control + shift + b -> international1
command + option + control + shift + o -> international3
